'''Rrudobar''' was one of the smaller of the twenty [[Space station/Legends|orbital cities]] of [[Duro/Legends|Duro]]. It contained the [[Event Horizon (Duro)|Event Horizon]] [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]].<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

==History==
The city was destroyed in [[26 ABY/Legends|26 ABY]] when the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Battle of Duro (Yuuzhan Vong War)|attacked]] Duro during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].<ref name="Balance Point">''[[The New Jedi Order: Balance Point]]''</ref>

